title: Politics of Texas
added: Texas is a Republican state as of 2020. Republicans control the overwhelming majority of land area in Texas and dominate rural Texas as well as mid-sized cities to the metropolitan suburbs as well. There are only a small handful of democrat counties in Texas, however, even these democrat run counties such as Harris, Bexar, Tarrant, and Dallas all have hundreds of thousands of loyal Texan Republicans. Texas Republicans and many mainstream news media companies predict Texas will stay Republican for the foreseeable future. <ref>https://www.politico.com/election-results/2018/texas/</ref> <ref>https://www.wsj.com/articles/how-the-democrats-will-keep-texas-red-11571872390</ref>
